{"type": "article", "id": 55895, "title": "一款预留充电口的皮套，帮你收纳无线耳机｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-08-02T22:49:42Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 52357, "name": "Blu Dot"}, {"id": 52358, "name": "Knindustrie"}, {"id": 52166, "name": "Saba Italia"}, {"id": 52359, "name": "Hi Thanks Bye"}, {"id": 33587, "name": "Twelve South"}, {"id": 52360, "name": "Jonghwan Kim"}, {"id": 52361, "name": "Sergio Bicego"}, {"id": 52362, "name": "Marco Zito"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 175, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180802210853KxkH0c8NM7sEdUGT.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>AirSnap for AirPods by Twelve South</h3><p>许多用 AirPods 无线耳机的用户，既感受到了其便捷性，也注意到它不好收纳、容易丢失的缺点。</p><p>最近，专为苹果产品设计周边配件的品牌 Twelve South 推出了一款专为 AirPods 量身制作的皮套 AirSnap，采用真皮制成，贴合 AirPods 尺寸的同事，也可以挂扣在裤子上，还细心地在下方预留了位置供充电之用，不用将其从皮套拿出来再进行充电。售价 29.99 美元，<a href=\"https://www.twelvesouth.com/product/airsnap\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802211008sSBNgHoZWwt4dYzm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802211008MvIdfC6cWTiHBUq5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802211009Xtkezqm8vDJOEgS5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802211009QicetA9q3fVx6znk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.twelvesouth.com/product/airsnap\" rel=\"nofollow\">Twelve South</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Collection 0 by Hi Thanks Bye</h3><p>多伦多设计师 Stein Wang 和 Topher Kong 成立了设计工作室 Hi Thanks Bye，并推出其首个系列 Collection 0，将于下月的伦敦设计节上首发。</p><p>Collection 0 的灵感源自加拿大自然风景与中式美学的融合，其中既能看到 Algonquin 公园、布鲁斯半岛和福戈岛的影子，又结合了融合岩石、植物、水的中式传统园林特征。</p><p>这个系列由粉末涂层不锈钢制成，包括书架、吧台凳、餐椅、边桌、落地灯和地毯，地毯是与纺织品设计师 Avis Ho 合作设计的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018080221110370j5wsYe9HyDgvST.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802211103vaWnRrwodiLO9Tpx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802211103S3Hai9Y2m17o5Cce.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802211103Y4jZgkf8zyS6Xoct.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802211104zYCUt67iWdV2olge.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802211104Nio3YFW2Xwx5Hdpf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802211104fPiWHluJ20Rr4znc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.hithanksbye.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hi Thanks Bye</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>New York Soleil &amp; Shades of Venice by Sergio Bicego &amp; Marco Zito for Saba Italia</h3><p>意大利家具品牌 Saba Italia 推出两个色彩丰富的户外编织家具系列。Sergio Bicego 操刀设计的 New York Soleil 系列是一组座椅，Marco Zito 设计的 Shades of Venice 系列则是屏风。虽然两个系列是不同的人设计的，但它们互为补充。</p><p>New York Soleil 系列是在金属结构的座椅上覆盖着色彩丰富的织物，耐用、快干、不吸水，整个系列包括沙发、扶手椅、坐垫、凳子等等。Shades of Venice 系列采用航海绳编织的超大框架，创造出格纹状图案，灵感来自威尼斯群岛的色彩。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802211149DhGeCnHo1b2vYVug.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201808022111498NOV01zUqfsHkpBr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2018080221114798Bxs0ekvFmQqKRp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802211152clyBLHtrpWq5KJZe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802211152h74yIlCfrWavjFPS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://sabaitalia.it/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Saba Italia</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Memo Cube by Jonghwan Kim</h3><p>韩国 Tale Studio 的设计师 Jonghwan Kim 对于桌面收纳很是关注，之前就曾推出过一系列小巧的桌面收纳筒，可以固定在显示器边缘。</p><p>最近，他又推出了新款收纳产品 Memo Cube，集合了四种不同类型的便利贴，确保用户拥有适合任何场合的便利贴。除此之外，它还为用户提供了一个专门的存放松散回形针的地方。所有这一切都包含在一个简洁但极其实用的方盒种，并且有多种颜色可供选择，既是桌面收纳的利器，也是一款简洁的桌面装饰物。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802211438k9B13KyiZdGQSh8X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802211438N4hKG9OJgUXnZfHF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802211439vTdH7sZAECLmWigQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802211439RDFjaUSgMHsfdmLc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802211439o1ghAL5S9nzmbItd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802211439mwrg6XDGzhonVPJs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.742857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"http://www.yankodesign.com/2018/08/01/you-will-never-forget-a-meeting-again/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yanko Design</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>The Omelette by Knindustrie</h3><p>意大利厨具品牌 Knindustrie 推出了一款煎蛋平底锅 The Omelette，打破常规，以方形结构呈现。操刀设计的 Lara Caffi 据说是受传统日本文化的启发，让人想到用于煎炸鸡蛋和便当的 Tamagoyaki 锅。不锈钢锅具均匀分布热量，木质手柄设计得也很巧妙。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201808022115246ymz3RlusNcGtAxj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.525781\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802211525YD72bJg01kHvtuSa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.588281\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201808022115256uX9Hg8lyWqACVZ5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201808022115251nxvKkXqBWyEuVHl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667014\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201808022115250GeLHXUOhPkiz51J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.897656\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://magazine.designbest.com/en/inspiration/accessories/the-omelette-by-knIndustrie-the-square-omelette-pan/\" rel=\"nofollow\">magazine.designbest.com</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Splash Coat Rack by Blu Dot</h3><p>美国现代家具品牌 Blu Dot 推出新款衣架 Splash。这是一款用粉末涂层钢材和坚实的胡桃木材组合构成的衣架。不管是把外衣、帽子、围巾和包包挂在衣架上，还是让其保持干净清爽的什么都不挂的状态，都是家中一处吸引目光的存在。售价 329 美元，<a href=\"https://www.bludot.com/splash-coat-rack.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180802211629TR2x4Fm9pK8hqGPd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201808022116309nYuWmaCBfGUwb1N.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}